description: Bluestone Resources Inc. engages in the exploration and development of mineral properties. Its flagship property is the 100% owned Cerro Blanco gold project located in southeastern Guatemala. The company was formerly known as Indicator Minerals Inc. and changed its name to Bluestone Resources Inc. in January 2012. Bluestone Resources Inc. was incorporated in 2000 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Peter Timothy Hemstead CMA, CPA
